              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COIN",
                "SI",
                "PS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " dE detector 20 mu-m thick, E -detector",
                " 1000 um thick. The angular positions and the",
                " energies of the two ejectiles, alpha and 3H, were",
                " detected in coincidence using two position- sensitive",
                " silicon detectors (PSDs, single area, resistive",
                " readout) having a spatial resolution of 0.5 mm.",
                " The two detectors were placed on opposite sides with",
